{
  "stem": "1692.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "And one day, a policeman, a friend of theirs came to the house and recognized her.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "The reason he didn't make trouble for the families because they were his friends.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "So he said, I'm leaving, but when I come back here, I don't want to see her here again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "So she left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Of course, she denied being Jewish, but she left and she came to me, and my farmer couldn't keep her there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "So he gave her a few leads and told her to go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to do with myself because I felt very guilty.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "So I decided to go with her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "But she made it easy for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "She said, two-- nobody will hire two people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "You stay here and I'll go to the people he is telling me to go.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "After that, I did not see my sister until the war was over.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "I-- the-- the Ukrainian Banderovcis started to kill the Poles, for whom they had no love either.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Because you see the Germans promised them an independent Ukraine if they help them with the Jewish problem.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "But after there were no more Jews, they said to them, there's not gonna be an independent Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And that's when they formed a partisan group called Banderovcis, after their leader, Bandera, and killing a hiding Jew whenever they could find one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the people I was staying with had to leave the village because they were Poles.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that Pentecostal farmer used to have, call it a meeting house where he lived.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "People from different-- different denominations would come to the house to pray.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were Protestants, Pentecostals, Seven Day Adventists, Evangelists, all kinds.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I never even knew they existed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they used to speak in tongues.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's all they have, the two rooms.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
